We may change this Notice. Please review the “Last Updated” legend at the top of this Notice to see when this Notice was last revised. Any changes to this Notice will become effective when we post the revised Notice on this Site. We encourage you to look for updates and changes to this Notice by checking this date when you access our Sites and services.
